			<td width="100%" height="25">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p166817">How copyright affects emulators</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=166817&amp;sid=df6bb171f9426a6c413a1131123a849a#p166817"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Fri Mar 25, 2016 10:16 am&nbsp;</div></td>
				</tr>
				</table>
